These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: domino, whist, monopoly, billiard
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, coral, mauve, lilac
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, camping, board-games, dancing
There 4 different types of food: orange, tomato, papaya, cherry
1. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing billiard##2
3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person eating orange##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating orange##1
5. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the person eating papaya is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
9. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Game   | whist | billiard   | domino  | monopoly  |
| Color   | coral    | lilac    | turquise      | mauve    |
| Hobby   | dancing | camping | board-games | chess |
| Food     | cherry  | orange       | tomato    | papaya     |

