.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, house, punk, salsa
There 4 different types of food: papaya, broccoli, pomegranate, apple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, tiparillo, chaman, dannemann
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, electrician, nurse, accountant
1. the accountant is on the right of the fan salsa##1
2. the fan dubstep is on the far right##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is the electrician##1
4. the fan punk is on the right of the fan house##1
5. the person eating apple is between the chaman-smoker and the paramedic##2
6. the accountant is between the person eating apple and the dannemann-smoker##2
7. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the fan punk##1
9. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre         | salsa | house    | punk  | dubstep    |
| Food   | papaya      | broccoli  | apple  | pomegranate |
| Cigar           | dannemann      | chaman       | tiparillo      | aristoff       |
| Job         | electrician    | accountant | nurse | paramedic |

