There are 4 different nationalities: italian, canadian, german, argentine
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, game, old-henry, ritmeester
1. the person playing backgammon is the game-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the left of the german##1
6. the person playing monopoly is the argentine##1
7. the person who likes amber is on the right of the german##1
8. the person who likes grey is between the italian and the argentine##2
9. the german is between the person who likes brown and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color        | mauve | brown     | grey   | amber     |
| Nationality       | canadian   | italian   | german | argentine |
| Game         | scrabble   | backgammon | mah-jongg       | monopoly    |
| Cigar   | old-henry    | game | blend  | ritmeester    |

