 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating pineapple is the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person eating lime is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is between the prince-smoker and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Beverage           | juice  | water | lemonade     | iced-tea |
| Food   | pineapple | peas  | grapefruit | lime       |
