 6. the pakistani is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the canadian##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the pakistani is between the person who likes blood-red and the person driving the tram##2
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality          | british         | pakistani         | canadian     | polish      |
